hemselves. Some get distracted from th=\r\ne journey and pursue the fruits actively. Collecting fruits is neither nece=\r\nssary nor sufficient for reaching the top. Though having a fruit that is av=\r\nailable only at a very high altitude shows that one has reached great altit=\r\nude, it cannot be used as a measure of one&#39;s progress, for someone may have=\r\n climbed greater heights without collecting that (or any) fruit. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/d=\r\niv&gt;&lt;div align=3D&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;=\r\n&nbsp; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=3D&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Ver=\r\ndana&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;External and internal do NOT have a one-to-one corresponde=\r\nnce. Just as you cannot tell what is inside a house by looking at it from o=\r\nutside, so cannot you tell one&#39;s state of mind from looking at one. One&#39;s s=\r\npiritual maturity and attainment is in one&#39;s state of mind. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;d=\r\niv\n align=3D&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;&nbs=\r\np; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=3D&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana=\r\n&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=\r\n;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=3D&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D=\r\n&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;&nbsp; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=3D&quot;LEF=\r\nT&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;&gt; If a loved and =\r\nrevered spiritual figure is percieved to be questioned, &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div a=\r\nlign=3D&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot; size=3D&qu